         <abstract>
            <p>We propose a way of extending the discontinuous Galerkin method from pure hyperbolic equations to convection-dominated equations with an O(h) diffusion term. The resulting method is explicit and can be applied with polynomials of degree n ≥ 1. The extended method satisfies the same O(h&lt;sup&gt;n + 1/2&lt;/sup&gt;) error estimate previously established for the discontinuous Galerkin method as applied to hyperbolic problems. Numerical results are provided.</p>
          </abstract>
